<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ارْتَابُوا}</span> ... شَكُّوا فِي النُّبُوَّةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَحِيفَ}</span> ... يَجُورَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جَهْدَ أَيْمَانِهِمْ}</span> ... مُجْتَهِدِينَ فِي الحَلِفِ والأَيْمَانِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{طَاعَةٌ مَّعْرُوفَةٌ}</span> ... طَاعَتُكُمْ مَعْرُوفَةٌ بِأَنَّهَا بِاللَّسَانِ فَقَطْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَلَيْهِ مَا حُمِّلَ}</span> ... عَلَى الرَّسُولِ فِعْلُ مَا أُمِرَ بِهِ مِنْ تَبْلِيغِ الرَّسَالَةِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَعَلَيْكُم مَّا حُمِّلْتُمْ}</span> ... عَلَيْكُمْ فِعْلُ مَا كُلِّفْتُمْ بِهِ مِنَ الاِمْتِثَالِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُعْجِزِينَ}</span> ... فَائِتِينَ مِنَ العَذَابِ بِالهَرَبِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٥٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَمْ يَبْلُغُوا الْحُلُمَ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> دُونَ سِنِّ الاِحْتِلَامِ، وَالبُلُوغِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جُنَاحٌ}</span> ... حَرَجٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْقَوَاعِدُ}</span> ... العَجَائِزُ مِنَ النِّسَاءِ اللَّاتِي قَعَدْنَ عَنِ الحَيْضِ، وَالوَلَدِ، وَالاِسْتِمْتَاعِ؛ لِكِبَرِهِنَّ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُتَبَرِّجَاتٍ}</span> ... مُظْهِرَاتٍ لِلزِّينَةِ الخَفِيَّةِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٦١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا مَلَكْتُم مَّفَاتِحَهُ}</span> ... البَيُوتِ الَّتِي وُكِّلْتُمْ بِحِفْظِهَا فِي غَيْبَةِ أَصْحَابِهَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
